78
00:05:20,525 --> 00:05:22,125
You...

79
00:05:22,525 --> 00:05:24,100
Come up with a way to hand both this military seal

80
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:26,150
and this decree to Zhao Zongquan.

81
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,400
The Imperial city

82
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,875
has already been surrounded by the rebel army.

83
00:05:32,325 --> 00:05:33,485
