95
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,450
I'm willing to deliver the decree.

96
00:06:21,450 --> 00:06:23,400
Who's talking?

97
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,875
I'm willing to deliver the Imperial decree.

98
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:34,350
How old are you?

99
00:06:34,650 --> 00:06:35,900
Thirteen.

100
00:06:36,925 --> 00:06:38,475
With such a young age

101
00:06:38,850 --> 00:06:40,475
and a weak build,

102
00:06:40,825 --> 00:06:42,600
how can you charge out of the

103
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,900
enclosure of the rebel army?

104
00:06:44,525 --> 00:06:45,875
I know the small alleys in the palace.

105
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:48,700
His Majesty doesn't like extravagance,

106
00:06:49,525 --> 00:06:50,393
so there are palace walls that

107
00:06:50,393 --> 00:06:51,150
haven't been repaired for a long time.

108
00:06:51,875 --> 00:06:52,941
Some dogs have created holes

109
00:06:52,941 --> 00:06:54,025
for them in a lot of walls.

110
00:06:54,575 --> 00:06:55,800
My build is small,

111
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:58,100
so I'll be able to crawl out of these dog holes.

112
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:00,375
Raise your head up.

113
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,825
Are you not afraid?

114
00:07:08,650 --> 00:07:10,100
When I initially entered the palace,

115
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:12,000
the Tea Brewing Eunuch asked me to

116
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,875
deliver tea to His Majesty.

117
00:07:13,775 --> 00:07:14,861
One day, when I was on duty

118
00:07:14,861 --> 00:07:15,875
to attend to His Majesty,

119
00:07:15,875 --> 00:07:17,124
I forgot to ground the tea leaves

120
00:07:17,124 --> 00:07:18,075
but didn't get discovered.

121
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:20,575
I thought that I was just fortunate.

122
00:07:20,900 --> 00:07:22,475
Afterwards, I learned that

123
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,975
His Majesty was actually very thirsty that day.

124
00:07:24,275 --> 00:07:26,000
However, he saw that I wasn't

125
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,325
carrying any tea with me,

126
00:07:27,475 --> 00:07:28,325
and just endured his thirst

127
00:07:28,325 --> 00:07:29,350
and didn't say anything throughout.

128
00:07:29,775 --> 00:07:31,650
Upon reaching his chamber palace,

129
00:07:31,650 --> 00:07:33,100
he drank all the tea

130
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:34,150
of Her Highness.

131
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,550
I've received great grace from His Majesty

132
00:07:36,875 --> 00:07:37,950
and was able to escape punishment.

133
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,750
Now, I'm willing to risk my life to repay him.

134
00:07:40,075 --> 00:07:41,975
It's because I saw how young you were,

135
00:07:42,025 --> 00:07:43,425
and couldn't bear for you to get punished.

136
00:07:43,725 --> 00:07:44,800
You shouldn't have remembered

137
00:07:45,350 --> 00:07:46,975
such a trifling matter for this long.

138
00:07:47,375 --> 00:07:48,825
For Your Majesty, it's just a trifling matter,

139
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:50,500
but for me, it's a major favor.

140
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,200
Just one word from Your Majesty,

141
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:53,625
and my life was saved.

142
00:07:54,050 --> 00:07:54,750
I'm willing to resolve

143
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:56,025
your urgent need.

144
00:07:56,350 --> 00:07:57,300
Okay. Okay.

145
00:07:57,900 --> 00:07:58,600
Lift your head up.

146
00:07:59,650 --> 00:08:00,825
You know how to repay the good deeds done to you.

147
00:08:01,275 --> 00:08:03,075
If you're able to deliver this letter out,

148
00:08:03,350 --> 00:08:05,557
you will earn the top meritorious deed

149
00:08:05,557 --> 00:08:07,000
in rescuing His Majesty!

150
00:08:11,050 --> 00:08:12,575
