234
00:13:25,850 --> 00:13:27,225
That's great.

235
00:13:28,850 --> 00:13:31,300
When you find Yuzhou's Militia Commander,

236
00:13:31,900 --> 00:13:33,350
ask him to use the military seal

237
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:36,000
and come to His Majesty's aid.

238
00:13:40,925 --> 00:13:42,400
They're not here.

239
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,750
Did you see

240
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:45,050
