241
00:13:45,825 --> 00:13:46,975
Upstairs.

242
00:13:47,375 --> 00:13:48,675
Quickly go after them!

243
00:13:49,175 --> 00:13:50,575
Hurry and leave!

244
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:52,175
Hurry and leave!

245
00:13:52,850 --> 00:13:53,450
