255
00:14:42,375 --> 00:14:43,625
Don't run!

256
00:14:44,175 --> 00:14:45,450
Hurry! Hurry and chase her!

257
00:14:45,450 --> 00:14:46,350
Quickly go after her! Hurry!

258
00:14:50,075 --> 00:14:51,025
Quickly go after her!

259
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:59,150
My horse carriage!

260
00:15:02,025 --> 00:15:03,650
Move aside!

261
00:15:26,050 --> 00:15:27,350
After her!

262
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:43,825
