280
00:17:58,500 --> 00:17:59,525
We only need to

281
00:17:59,525 --> 00:18:00,800
guard by my father's side.

282
00:18:14,625 --> 00:18:15,350
Idiot!

283
00:18:16,325 --> 00:18:19,300
