Don't be afraid.

288
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:03,175
Second Uncle!

289
00:19:03,175 --> 00:19:04,250
They're all dead.

290
00:19:09,525 --> 00:19:11,225
Why are you here?

291
00:19:11,225 --> 00:19:12,600
I'm going to Bianjing.

292
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,550
I'm going to Yuzhou.

293
00:19:15,350 --> 00:19:16,825
Why are you going there?

294
00:19:16,825 --> 00:19:17,950
I...I am going to

295
00:19:18,325 --> 00:19:19,900
look for Zhao Zongquan.

296
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:22,700
I'm going to hand him the military seal and...

297
00:19:23,250 --> 00:19:24,300
the blood-written decree.

298
00:19:25,050 --> 00:19:27,425
Quickly take him to look for him.

299
00:19:28,525 --> 00:19:30,750
What military seal? What blood-written decree?

300
00:19:33,775 --> 00:19:36,000
You...have a horse.

301
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:36,975
I have no time to explain.

302
00:19:36,975 --> 00:19:37,800
Quickly take me there.

303
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:39,200
Stop! He's just over there.

304
00:19:41,275 --> 00:19:42,300
Over there.

305
00:19:42,650 --> 00:19:44,250
Zhao Zongquan.

306
00:19:50,675 --> 00:19:52,075
Officer!

307
00:20:07,525 --> 00:20:09,625
Is that indeed His Majesty's handwriting?

308
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:10,675
Right.

309
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,925
Although he wrote it with his finger,

310
00:20:15,125 --> 00:20:16,500
this robe fabric must be his.

311
00:20:18,050 --> 00:20:19,500
Since that's the case,

312
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:21,575
Father is now the Crown Prince

313
00:20:21,650 --> 00:20:23,150
conferred by His Majesty.

314
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:27,850
Don't!

315
00:20:29,825 --> 00:20:31,550
Quickly get up.Don't bow to me!

316
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:34,850
This is a good thing.

317
00:20:35,275 --> 00:20:36,425
Your Highness, there's no need to panic.

318
00:20:36,775 --> 00:20:38,800
What do you mean, 'Your Highness'? What "Highness"!

319
00:20:39,350 --> 00:20:40,500
Don't even mention those two words.

320
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,600
I'm panicking!

321
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:45,000
Don't talk about some "crown prince" now!

322
00:20:45,225 --> 00:20:46,325
Quickly go save the Emperor!

323
00:20:46,875 --> 00:20:47,512
With just a few of us,

324
00:20:47,512 --> 00:20:48,575
how are we going to save His Majesty?

325
00:20:49,600 --> 00:20:51,025
We must take the Imperial decree

326
00:20:51,325 --> 00:20:52,850
and mobilize the army

327
00:20:52,850 --> 00:20:54,250
under the command of the Crown Prince.

328
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:56,575
Lord, stop delaying!

329
00:20:57,225 --> 00:20:58,000
If we delay it any longer,

330
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,300
I fear that His Majesty might be dead by then!

331
00:20:59,300 --> 00:20:59,662
When the father dies,

332
00:20:59,662 --> 00:21:00,211
the son ascends to the throne!

333
00:21:00,211 --> 00:21:00,700
That's just right and proper!

334
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:04,425
As an Imperial relative,

335
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:05,753
being entrusted with such a mission

336
00:21:05,753 --> 00:21:06,225
during this dangerous time

337
00:21:06,225 --> 00:21:07,350
and forcing myself to ascend to the position

338
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:08,625
will surely cause myself future trouble!

339
00:21:14,125 --> 00:21:16,875
Father, how could you say such words?

340
00:21:17,150 --> 00:21:19,075
The current Emperor has no sons!

341
00:21:19,425 --> 00:21:20,775
Now, he even made a decree.

342
00:21:20,775 --> 00:21:21,348
Everything is being done

343
00:21:21,348 --> 00:21:22,000
and perfectly justifiable!

344
00:21:22,325 --> 00:21:23,550
How could there be future troubles?

345
00:21:23,975 --> 00:21:25,325
Have you

346
00:21:25,525 --> 00:21:26,550
forgotten the ancestors

347
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:27,950
of Zhao clan killing each other?

348
00:21:33,175 --> 00:21:34,725
If in the end,

349
00:21:35,450 --> 00:21:36,900
brothers will be fighting,

350
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:37,709
father and sons will

351
00:21:37,709 --> 00:21:38,275
turn hostile to each other,

352
00:21:38,525 --> 00:21:39,600
there's no point

353
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:40,950
in becoming crown prince.

354
00:21:42,300 --> 00:21:44,200
I'm already satisfied

355
00:21:44,475 --> 00:21:45,200
to live my life

356
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,075
in peace.

357
00:21:48,450 --> 00:21:50,350
Please just spare me this.

358
00:21:58,255 --> 00:21:58,976
Lord,

359
00:22:00,493 --> 00:22:01,587
the reason that Prince Yan wanted to assassinate

360
00:22:01,587 --> 00:22:02,042
the person carrying

361
00:22:02,042 --> 00:22:02,830
the blood-written Imperial decree

362
00:22:03,253 --> 00:22:04,993
must be because he knows what's written on it.

363
00:22:05,416 --> 00:22:06,186
Do you think

364
00:22:06,708 --> 00:22:08,001
he'll let us go back to Yuzhou

365
00:22:08,001 --> 00:22:08,896
and live our days in peace?

366
00:22:10,288 --> 00:22:11,407
Just one entrusted Imperial decree

367
00:22:11,780 --> 00:22:13,197
has already invited

368
00:22:13,197 --> 00:22:14,191
so many assassins.

369
00:22:14,788 --> 00:22:16,280
Once Prince Yan learns that

370
00:22:16,280 --> 00:22:16,788
His Majesty has intentions

371
00:22:16,788 --> 00:22:17,374
of passing the throne to you,

372
00:22:17,647 --> 00:22:18,003
no matter if he chases you

373
00:22:18,003 --> 00:22:18,368
to the end of the world,

374
00:22:18,692 --> 00:22:20,382
he will cut the weeds and dig up the roots!

375
00:22:22,495 --> 00:22:24,410
Prince Yan is so ruthless.

376
00:22:25,031 --> 00:22:25,759
He's even able to do such a thing

377
00:22:25,759 --> 00:22:26,498
as forcing the Emperor to abdicate.

378
00:22:26,498 --> 00:22:27,120
Do you think

379
00:22:27,120 --> 00:22:29,233
he will let your whole family go?

380
00:22:30,824 --> 00:22:31,321
This...

381
00:22:33,111 --> 00:22:33,932
Now,

382
00:22:34,553 --> 00:22:36,020
your life is temporarily preserved,

383
00:22:36,890 --> 00:22:38,332
but the officials of Yuzhou

384
00:22:38,332 --> 00:22:39,401
will soon lose theirs!

385
00:22:39,724 --> 00:22:42,782
Lord, please immediately decide!

386
00:22:44,697 --> 00:22:47,059
Father, let's not talk about

387
00:22:47,059 --> 00:22:47,905
our lives first.

388
00:22:49,470 --> 00:22:51,509
We still have our wives and children in Yuzhou,

389
00:22:52,081 --> 00:22:53,274
that's several lives.

390
00:22:54,741 --> 00:22:56,531
My daughter is just

391
00:22:56,730 --> 00:22:58,445
two years old.

392
00:22:59,464 --> 00:23:01,777
If Father refuses to accept this Imperial decree,

393
00:23:03,094 --> 00:23:04,213
then those several lives

394
00:23:04,213 --> 00:23:05,655
in our family

395
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:08,365
will be gone.

396
00:23:10,801 --> 00:23:13,362
Father, I beg you to save me.

397
00:23:13,984 --> 00:23:15,450
Save our whole family.

398
00:23:20,174 --> 00:23:21,343
Lord,

399
00:23:21,790 --> 00:23:22,934
while Prince Yan

400
00:23:22,934 --> 00:23:24,003
still has no free hand to spare,

401
00:23:24,003 --> 00:23:25,842
we can knock him cold

402
00:23:25,867 --> 00:23:27,135
and battle it out with him.

403
00:23:27,334 --> 00:23:28,453
If we delay it any further,

404
00:23:28,801 --> 00:23:30,417
until Prince Yan forced His Majesty

405
00:23:30,417 --> 00:23:31,362
to amend the decree,

406
00:23:31,362 --> 00:23:32,506
we will never

407
00:23:33,003 --> 00:23:34,096
be able to

408
00:23:34,096 --> 00:23:35,887
resist him.

409
00:23:35,887 --> 00:23:36,757
Lord!

410
00:23:41,853 --> 00:23:44,165
Didn't you already address me as 'Your Highness'?

411
00:23:45,210 --> 00:23:47,024
Why are you still calling me "Lord'?

412
00:23:52,295 --> 00:23:53,662
May Your Highness give your orders!

413
00:23:54,383 --> 00:23:55,627
Go change clothes.

414
00:23:55,900 --> 00:23:58,063
Take the blood-written decree and military seal

415
00:23:58,063 --> 00:23:58,995
to mobilize the army at the main military camp

416
00:23:58,995 --> 00:23:59,778
at the western outskirts of the city.

417
00:24:02,836 --> 00:24:04,626
Enter the capital and pacify the rebellion!

418
00:24:06,292 --> 00:24:08,182
Your Highness is wise!

419
00:24:25,435 --> 00:24:26,877
The two of us are really fated.

420
00:24:28,096 --> 00:24:29,513
When you encounter danger and need to be saved,

421
00:24:29,513 --> 00:24:30,731
you will always bump into me.

422
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:33,242
You are

423
00:24:33,242 --> 00:24:34,112
my life-preserving deity.

424
00:24:35,579 --> 00:24:36,723
Once I get home,

425
00:24:36,996 --> 00:24:37,543
I surely will make you a tablet

426
00:24:37,543 --> 00:24:38,537
to pray for your long life.

427
00:24:39,432 --> 00:24:40,328
I must light an incense stick for it

428
00:24:40,328 --> 00:24:41,869
and kowtow to you every day.

429
00:24:44,430 --> 00:24:45,698
How come that didn't sound like

430
00:24:45,698 --> 00:24:46,667
you were thanking me?

431
00:24:48,582 --> 00:24:49,775
No matter how many thanks I say,

432
00:24:49,775 --> 00:24:51,043
all are just empty words.

433
00:24:51,540 --> 00:24:52,311
If there are deities,

434
00:24:52,584 --> 00:24:53,479
they surely will give me

435
00:24:54,001 --> 00:24:55,069
another chance to repay you.

436
00:24:55,866 --> 00:24:57,159
How?

437
00:24:58,302 --> 00:24:59,694
Use my life to repay you.

438
00:25:03,822 --> 00:25:05,637
Why would I want your life?

439
00:25:06,681 --> 00:25:07,128
This...

440
00:25:07,675 --> 00:25:08,148
There aren't that many people

441
00:25:08,148 --> 00:25:09,067
in this world

442
00:25:09,341 --> 00:25:10,212
who could make me pay them with my life.

443
00:25:10,212 --> 00:25:11,554
My mother was one.

444
00:25:11,554 --> 00:25:12,772
My grandmother is another one.

445
00:25:13,344 --> 00:25:15,557
Second Uncle Gu, you're the third one.

446
00:25:18,714 --> 00:25:19,957
What about your future husband?

447
00:25:21,274 --> 00:25:22,194
How would I know about

448
00:25:22,269 --> 00:25:23,611
such a faraway thing?

449
00:25:25,277 --> 00:25:27,465
You don't know, but I do.

450
00:25:28,981 --> 00:25:30,622
You...what do you know?

451
00:25:34,028 --> 00:25:36,017
I know that you have sprained your foot.

452
00:25:36,017 --> 00:25:37,758
You have to recuperate for a few days.

453
00:25:38,578 --> 00:25:39,771
Luckily, you didn't hurt your bone.

454
00:25:40,691 --> 00:25:41,686
This will be healed in a few days.

455
00:25:42,531 --> 00:25:43,948
Don't expose the wound on your hand to water.

456
00:25:44,570 --> 00:25:45,589
I'll leave Shitou to accompany you.

457
00:25:46,559 --> 00:25:47,777
If I successfully pacify the rebellion,

458
00:25:49,119 --> 00:25:50,238
I will light two fireworks.

459
00:25:51,382 --> 00:25:52,848
Tell Shitou then to take you to the palace

460
00:25:52,848 --> 00:25:54,116
to reunite with your father and brother.

461
00:25:54,813 --> 00:25:55,683
If I fail,

462
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:58,119
I will just light one firework.

463
00:25:59,462 --> 00:26:00,804
At that time,

464
00:26:00,829 --> 00:26:02,097
let Shitou take you to

465
00:26:02,097 --> 00:26:02,793
your Sheng Manor in Jiying Alley by daybreak.

466
00:26:04,633 --> 00:26:06,398
I can see the fireworks and can walk.

467
00:26:06,870 --> 00:26:07,200
You, however,

468
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,188
will be in a very dangerous situation.

469
00:26:08,462 --> 00:26:10,177
How about you take Shitou with you instead?

470
00:26:12,414 --> 00:26:13,633
Are you...

471
00:26:14,876 --> 00:26:16,144
worried about me?

472
00:26:16,467 --> 00:26:17,660
Will you die?

473
00:26:30,563 --> 00:26:32,577
Blades have no eyes. Be careful!

474
00:26:33,621 --> 00:26:34,864
Say something auspicious for me to hear!

475
00:26:36,257 --> 00:26:37,177
It's time to go!

476
00:26:42,223 --> 00:26:44,187
Then I...I will wait for your return!

477
00:26:49,135 --> 00:26:51,472
With you waiting, I surely will return!

478
00:26:55,947 --> 00:26:57,414
I... I...I

479
00:26:57,414 --> 00:26:58,533
didn't mean it that way.

480
00:27:24,438 --> 00:27:25,259
I stayed behind

481
00:27:25,259 --> 00:27:26,850
not really to accompany you, Miss.

482
00:27:27,844 --> 00:27:29,187
I stayed behind to make my Young Master

483
00:27:29,187 --> 00:27:29,933
feel at ease.

484
00:27:48,628 --> 00:27:49,822
Who are the people outside the city walls?

485
00:27:50,443 --> 00:27:51,155
I'm the commander of the main military camp

486
00:27:51,155 --> 00:27:51,662
in the western city outskirt,

487
00:27:51,662 --> 00:27:54,123
Shenwei General Song Zhao Zhong!

488
00:27:55,242 --> 00:27:56,261
I was decreed to enter the capital!

489
00:27:56,733 --> 00:27:57,280
We just received orders

490
00:27:57,280 --> 00:27:58,126
from the Defense Chief of the palace

491
00:27:58,623 --> 00:27:59,940
to close the city gates ahead of time,

492
00:28:00,264 --> 00:28:01,830
and no one is allowed to enter the city!

493
00:28:02,228 --> 00:28:03,545
Where's your Imperial decree?

494
00:28:03,968 --> 00:28:05,236
Who ordered you?

495
00:28:10,333 --> 00:28:12,422
It was Prince Yan who delivered me a letter!

496
00:28:12,819 --> 00:28:13,724
He told us to enter the city

497
00:28:13,724 --> 00:28:14,609
and wait for further orders!

498
00:28:14,783 --> 00:28:15,987
Don't waste any more time!

499
00:28:15,987 --> 00:28:17,095
Quickly open the gates!

500
00:28:28,283 --> 00:28:29,725
Charge!

501
00:28:30,147 --> 00:28:31,366
Charge!

502
00:28:36,089 --> 00:28:37,605
Charge!

503
00:28:43,647 --> 00:28:46,705
It's easy for me to die.

504
00:28:49,837 --> 00:28:53,169
But without a conferment decree,

505
00:28:54,263 --> 00:28:56,525
you will then be unable to justify your claim.

506
00:28:57,296 --> 00:28:58,365
The descendants of the Imperial Zhao family

507
00:28:58,365 --> 00:29:00,155
can then launch a crusade against you.

508
00:29:00,453 --> 00:29:03,064
Let's see how long you can maintain your rule!

509
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:11,840
Your Highness!

510
00:29:11,840 --> 00:29:12,412
Your Majesty!

511
00:29:12,436 --> 00:29:12,984
Your Highness.

512
00:29:12,984 --> 00:29:14,699
Your Highness, don't be rash.

513
00:29:16,017 --> 00:29:18,031
We must have an Imperial decree for this to work.

514
00:29:23,972 --> 00:29:25,489
If he won't write it,

515
00:29:27,602 --> 00:29:29,119
I'll write it myself.

516
00:29:30,387 --> 00:29:31,381
Your Highness!

517
00:29:33,146 --> 00:29:34,340
Your Highness!

518
00:29:35,881 --> 00:29:36,776
Your Highness,

519
00:29:36,776 --> 00:29:37,457
the Imperial Army from outside

520
00:29:37,457 --> 00:29:38,093
has charged into the palace!

521
00:29:43,414 --> 00:29:45,453
I have the Emperor in my hands!

522
00:29:46,397 --> 00:29:48,013
Your Majesty!

523
00:29:48,685 --> 00:29:50,624
Who dares to make any rash moves!

524
00:29:53,209 --> 00:29:54,303
Your Highness...

525
00:30:01,687 --> 00:30:02,606
The mastermind of the rebellion,

526
00:30:02,606 --> 00:30:03,403
Prince Yan, is already dead!

527
00:30:03,452 --> 00:30:05,416
All of you, quickly surrender!

528
00:30:05,715 --> 00:30:06,809
Protect the Emperor!

529
00:31:07,918 --> 00:31:09,460
I was late to Your Majesty's defense.

530
00:31:09,460 --> 00:31:10,976
I caused Your Majesty to be startled.

531
00:31:15,426 --> 00:31:16,993
This is heaven's will.

532
00:31:19,529 --> 00:31:21,542
Prince Yan suffered from his own actions.

533
00:31:22,462 --> 00:31:23,830
If not because that child

534
00:31:23,929 --> 00:31:25,769
bumped into you when she went out of the city,

535
00:31:27,111 --> 00:31:28,270
the Empress and I

536
00:31:28,270 --> 00:31:30,468
would have died a long time ago.

537
00:31:32,456 --> 00:31:34,097
This is my duty.

538
00:31:38,001 --> 00:31:38,945
You.

539
00:31:40,835 --> 00:31:41,767
You entered the palace

540
00:31:41,767 --> 00:31:43,023
when you were eight years old.

541
00:31:43,818 --> 00:31:47,398
You once did a spear dance in front of me.

542
00:31:48,467 --> 00:31:49,835
After doing it,

543
00:31:50,307 --> 00:31:52,147
you asked me for some reward money.

544
00:31:55,603 --> 00:31:57,442
I've never seen a child

545
00:31:57,442 --> 00:31:58,710
as bold as you were.

546
00:31:59,133 --> 00:32:00,252
Out of joy,

547
00:32:00,426 --> 00:32:02,613
I gave you that spear.

548
00:32:04,379 --> 00:32:05,348
After that,

549
00:32:05,647 --> 00:32:07,338
you rarely entered the palace.

550
00:32:07,636 --> 00:32:09,227
I haven't seen you recently.

551
00:32:11,265 --> 00:32:12,508
You Majesty never forgets what you see.

552
00:32:12,832 --> 00:32:14,572
You are indeed a genius.

553
00:32:15,541 --> 00:32:16,809
Entered the palace?

554
00:32:17,754 --> 00:32:19,072
What do you mean, entered the palace?

555
00:32:20,812 --> 00:32:23,597
He's the second son of old Marquis Ningyuan.

556
00:32:24,342 --> 00:32:25,884
He used to frequently enter the palace.

557
00:32:29,663 --> 00:32:30,466
The House of Marquis Ningyuan

558
00:32:30,466 --> 00:32:31,714
have been meritorious officers for generations.

559
00:32:32,522 --> 00:32:34,536
No wonder you achieved such great military merits

560
00:32:34,536 --> 00:32:35,679
during the pacification of the southern rebellion.

561
00:32:37,196 --> 00:32:38,464
He has profound hereditary learning.

562
00:32:40,776 --> 00:32:42,143
I got expelled out of our house by my father,

563
00:32:42,466 --> 00:32:43,088
and my mother's surname is Bai.

564
00:32:43,983 --> 00:32:45,872
I didn't deliberately fool you, Commander.

565
00:32:46,071 --> 00:32:47,290
May you forgive me.

566
00:32:49,453 --> 00:32:51,417
Is your leg wound okay?

567
00:32:53,132 --> 00:32:54,002
Thank you, for Your Majesty's concerns.

568
00:32:55,146 --> 00:32:56,016
It's fine.

569
00:32:56,986 --> 00:32:58,552
You still mustn't neglect it.

570
00:32:59,546 --> 00:33:00,814
